title: Jungle Girl Omnibus
description: Taking you all the way from the genesis of the original series to the stunning conclusion of the first season to the exciting opening of the 2nd season of stories and more... Jungle Girl delivers action, excitement, twists, thrills, and the finest illustrations of dinosaurs and the female form found in comics today! Cho and Murray take the action underground and underwater as more clues regarding Jana, the undisputed Queen of the Jungle, finds out more about her mysterious past, and the mysterious island she calls home! Clocking in at over 230 pages, this omnibus collects issues #0-5 from the original Jungle Girl series, and issues #1-5 from Season Two. And let's not forget all the amazing Frank Cho and Adrian Batista covers!
author: Frank Cho
